---
---

<section class="how" id="how" aria-labelledby="how-heading">
  <div class="kicker">How it works</div>
  <h2 id="how-heading" class="reveal">No 40 page proposals.<br /><em>Just three steps.</em></h2>
  <div class="steps">

    <div class="step reveal">
      <div class="s-top">
        <div class="s-num">01</div>
        <div class="s-ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M21 11.5a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9 3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1-7.6 4.7 8.38 8.38 0 0 1-3.8-.9L3 21l1.9-5.7a8.38 8.38 0 0 1-.9-3.8 8.5 8.5 0 0 1 4.7-7.6 8.38 8.38 0 0 1 3.8-.9h.5a8.48 8.48 0 0 1 8 8v.5z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4>We talk. You vent.</h4>
      <p>A free 20 minute call. You tell us what eats your team's day. No pitch deck, promise.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step reveal">
      <div class="s-top">
        <div class="s-num">02</div>
        <div class="s-ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <polygon points="3 6 9 3 15 6 21 3 21 18 15 21 9 18 3 21 3 6" />
            <line x1="9" y1="3" x2="9" y2="18" />
            <line x1="15" y1="6" x2="15" y2="21" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4>We map it. You approve it.</h4>
      <p>A plain English plan. What we build, what it costs, what it saves. If the maths does not work, we say so.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step reveal">
      <div class="s-top">
        <div class="s-num">03</div>
        <div class="s-ico">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M4.5 16.5c-1.5 1.26-2 5-2 5s3.74-.5 5-2c.71-.84.7-2.13-.09-2.91a2.18 2.18 0 0 0-2.91-.09z" />
            <path d="M12 15l-3-3a22 22 0 0 1 2-3.95A12.88 12.88 0 0 1 22 2c0 2.72-.78 7.5-6 11a22.35 22.35 0 0 1-4 2z" />
            <path d="M9 12H4s.55-3.03 2-4c1.62-1.08 5 0 5 0" />
            <path d="M12 15v5s3.03-.55 4-2c1.08-1.62 0-5 0-5" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h4>We build. You forget it existed.</h4>
      <p>Shipped in weeks, not quarters. Then we stay, watch it run and keep tuning it.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how {
    padding: clamp(60px, 7vw, 100px) clamp(24px, 5vw, 72px) clamp(100px, 12vw, 160px);
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .kicker {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 2.6px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-purple-mid);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .kicker::before {
    content: '';
    width: 30px;
    height: 1.5px;
    background: var(--color-purple-mid);
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(38px, 5.4vw, 72px);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    line-height: 1.02;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
  }

  h2 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--color-purple-mid);
  }

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(24px, 4vw, 56px);
  }

  .step {
    border-top: 2px solid var(--color-ink);
    padding-top: 26px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .step:hover { border-color: var(--color-purple-mid); }

  .s-top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }

  .s-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--color-purple-mid);
  }

  .s-ico {
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--color-purple-soft);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .s-ico svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    stroke: var(--color-purple);
    fill: none;
    stroke-width: 1.7;
    stroke-linecap: round;
    stroke-linejoin: round;
    transition: stroke 0.3s;
  }

  .step:hover .s-ico {
    background: var(--color-purple);
    transform: rotate(-6deg) scale(1.06);
  }

  .step:hover .s-ico svg { stroke: #fff; }

  h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 2.2vw, 30px);
    letter-spacing: -0.4px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 15.5px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-muted);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
